  "channels": ["irc"],            // Declares which channels this plugin provides
  "configSchema": {               // JSON schema for plugin config discovery
    "type": "object",
    "additionalProperties": false,
    "properties": {}              // Usually empty - full schema in config-schema.ts
  }
}
```

#### **package.json** (NPM Package Definition)
Key sections for channel plugins:
```json
{
  "name": "@openclaw/irc",
  "openclaw": {
    "extensions": ["./index.ts"],           // Entry points to load
    "setupEntry": "./setup-entry.ts",      // Setup-time entry point
    "channel": {
      "id": "irc",                          // Must match openclaw.plugin.json
      "label": "IRC",                       // Human-readable name
      "selectionLabel": "IRC (Server + Nick)", // For UI selection
      "detailLabel": "IRC",                 // Detail display
      "docsPath": "/channels/irc",          // Doc location
      "docsLabel": "irc",                   // Doc ID
      "blurb": "classic IRC networks...",   // Short description
