- `DefinedChannelPluginEntry<TPlugin>` - Defined channel plugin entry type
- `CreateChannelPluginBaseOptions<TResolvedAccount>` - Options for channel plugin base
- `CreatedChannelPluginBase<TResolvedAccount>` - Created channel plugin base type
- `ChatChannelPluginBase<TResolvedAccount, Probe, Audit>` - Base type for chat channels
- `ChatChannelSecurityOptions<TResolvedAccount>` - Security configuration options
